{"tid":776444,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"笑死~ pre ocamp 差d整到個屋邨肥毒撚喊","createTime":"2018-08-12T05:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T06:13:00.000Z","uid":84710,"like":19,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"30a09e74687831c96a8cd121330ba505313cca08","tid":776444,"uid":84710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"我地約咗係又一城某間高級餐廳門口集合<br />\n因為要gel頭同埋襯衫 我最遲一個先到 <br />\n離遠望已經見到有嗰肥毒企係成堆人側邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先形容吓佢嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塊面又肥又油之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個頭仲好似岩岩瞓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n件衫仲衰! U記不得止<br />\n仲要大大隻米奇老鼠!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 救命!<br />\n最好笑係佢自己孤零零一個企係成班人側邊<br />\n完全無人理佢 其他人個個靚仔靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n著衫又潮 當然我都係其中一分子啦<br />\n<br />\n入到去餐廳  一開始介紹吓自己先<br />\n個嗰都用英文名介紹自己 好似Jessica, Jonathan, Fiona, Alexanda<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰肥毒竟然好自豪話叫自己做阿輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有嗰組爸笑鳩佢係咪愛回家個送水輝<br />\n嗰肥毒竟然嬲豬認真MODE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話大學生唔使做送水呢D粗重工作喎<br />\n我地全部人睇到眼到凸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地搞吓笑唔使咁認真呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個毒撚睇完餐牌嚇到鳩都縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫咗個最平嘅餐 最平都要$88 仲要另收加1<br />\n佢仲要唔加$38蚊嘅餐包餐湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到差唔多埋單<br />\n有囡囡話想食甜品 不如大家嗌幾個大家share <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁個個都話ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知個肥毒話減肥<br />\n問真d原來佢銀包得翻100蚊 嗌咗甜品就唔夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後佢好唔情願咁話不如今餐佢碌卡<br />\n大家再俾返錢佢<br />\n<br />\n去到埋單個陣笑到我地仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間餐廳話今日信用卡部機壞咗 要收返現金 <br />\n個肥毒即刻望住大家 呢個時候大家都呆咗唔知俾咩反應<br />\n好彩有個組媽好好人同個肥毒講 我幫你俾住先啦 你遲d先俾返我<br />\n食完飯之後 有人提議去city行返個圈 認識吓新環境<br />\n個肥毒就扮有事 一枝箭咁走咗<br />\n去到依家個group 佢都無出過聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6600282615e7dfd9af798755a110968e92af888","tid":776444,"uid":198822,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"你咪又係shitty仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94ab061834bcfb9a0c2a20189a2fa36103c5ca1","tid":776444,"uid":135445,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"bab709de450ad7a1eb07916f8467c49dde4b98c5","tid":776444,"uid":38604,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:54:46.000Z","msg":"Too long don't read"},{"pid":"dad784cddf2421f38000b8c7881f96dced724607","tid":776444,"uid":136038,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"出一篇假膠文有幾錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5852e36652542b4c9f73d8bf61d909e34e653181","tid":776444,"uid":158613,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"30a09e74687831c96a8cd121330ba505313cca08","